-------------------------------------------------------------------------
2.9 Troubleshooting Common Issues
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Check if forwarding is enabled
cat /proc/sys/net/ipv4/ip_forward
cat /proc/sys/net/ipv6/conf/all/forwarding

2. Check nftables rules
sudo nft list ruleset

3. Check NAT rules specifically
sudo nft list table ip nat

4. Check interface status
ip link show
ip addr show

5. Check routing tables
ip route show
ip -6 route show

6. Check if packets are being forwarded (view counters)
sudo nft list chain inet filter forward

7. Temporarily disable firewall for testing
sudo nft flush ruleset

8. Enable packet forwarding temporarily (if not set in sysctl.conf)
sudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.ip_forward=1

9. Add logging for debugging
sudo nft add rule inet filter forward log prefix "FW-FWD: " accept

10. View logs
sudo journalctl -kf | grep "FW-FWD"

